General Information

Rose Floral Water is created when fresh rose petals are distilled as part of the process of extracting pure Rose essential oil. Rose Floral Water is renowned as a skin toner, it is recommended for all skin types, especially dry & dehydrated. Enjoy the natural, alluring scent of pure Rose.

Warnings

STORE BELOW 30C. NOT TO BE TAKEN ORALLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.

Ingredients

Rosa damascena Water

Directions

Apply after cleansing or throughout the day to hydrate the skin. In summer keep in the refrigerator to cool and refresh.
